eded\\\": \\\"Please provide the full text of the candidate’s resume so that skills, experience, and education details can be accurately extracted.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 1\\nhere are some feedbacks:\\n- The output does not fulfill the task of extracting skills, experience, and education because no resume content was provided.\\n- Rather than returning empty arrays, we should clearly indicate that extraction cannot proceed and prompt the user for the resume.\\n- The field name “resume_needed” is non-standard; use a more explicit “error” or “message” key.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"Resume content missing\\\",\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"Please provide the full text of the candidate’s resume so that we can extract skills, experience, and education.\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"# **The Overall Goal**\\nYou are a workflow planning agent.\\nYour task is to:\\n-\\\"Analyze the job description\\\",\\n    \\\"Analyze the candidate resume\\\",\\n    \\\"Conduct technical interview\\\",\\n    \\\"Send emails as and when needed\\\",\\n    \\\"Score candidate responses\\\",\\n    \\\"Generate final evaluation report\\\"\\n\\nReturn the output as a .txt file of all the steps taken to perform the tasks.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nNo completed previous tasks context available.\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task3:\\n  Objective: Compose and send the interview invitation email to the candidate\\nTask task6:\\n  Objective: Compile a final evaluation report including resume summary and scored responses\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nExtract candidate's skills, experience, and education from the resume\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nJSON\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"Resume content missing\\\",\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"Please provide the full text of the candidate’s resume so that we can extract skills, experience, and education.\\\"\\n}\\n```\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-27T16:49:37.783342\"\n}"}
{"timestamp": "2026-05-27 16:49:39,025", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_gpt_conversation", "line": 403, "message": "{\n  \"event_type\": \"gpt_conversation\",\n  \"task_id\": \"task_7\",\n  \"conversation_type\": \"task_execution\",\n  \"iteration\": 1,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"\\n# Role:\\nHelp me produce a precise and detailed solution for the given task. Follow these instructions exactly:\\n\\n# Objective & Steps:\\n1. Ensure Completeness:\\n   - Avoid placeholders or incomplete text.\\n   - Your output must meet all requirements of the task.\\n   - Include all necessary details so that the output is self-contained and can be directly used as input for downstream tasks.\\n\\n2. Maintain Precision and Clarity:\\n   - Your output will be used as input for subsequent tasks; therefore, it must be comprehensive and precise.\\n   - **Output the answer only without any jusifications**\\n\\n3. Avoid Repetition:\\n   - Do not repeat verbatim any content from previous tasks.\\n   - Ensure your output is original and adds value to the workflow.\\n\\n\\n\\n# Audience:\\nYour output will be used as a solution for the given task, it will be used in the later validation and intergration process.\\n\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"# **The Overall Goal**\\nYou are a workflow planning agent.\\nYour task is to:\\n-\\\"Analyze the job description\\\",\\n    \\\"Analyze the candidate resume\\\",\\n    \\\"Conduct technical interview\\\",\\n    \\\"Send emails as and when needed\\\",\\n    \\\"Score candidate responses\\\",\\n    \\\"Generate final evaluation report\\\"\\n\\nReturn the output as a .txt file of all the steps taken to perform the tasks.\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n---\\n# **Context from Upstream Tasks**\\nTask task0:\\n  Objective: Extract key skills and requirements from the job description\\n  Result: ```json\\n{\\n  \\\"job_description_analysis\\\": {\\n    \\\"key_skills\\\": [\\n      \\\"Software Development\\\",\\n      \\\"Java\\\",\\n      \\\"Spring Framework\\\",\\n      \\\"RESTful API Design\\\",\\n      \\\"SQL Databases\\\",\\n      \\\"Git\\\",\\n      \\\"Agile/Scrum\\\",\\n      \\\"Unit Testing\\\",\\n      \\\"Microservices\\\",\\n      \\\"Problem-solving\\\",\\n      \\\"Debugging\\\",\\n      \\\"Communication\\\",\\n      \\\"Collaboration\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"requirements\\\": [\\n      \\\"Bachelor’s degree in Computer Science or related field\\\",\\n      \\\"3+ years of professional software engineering experience\\\",\\n      \\\"Experience designing and building microservices\\\",\\n      \\\"Strong problem-solving and debugging skills\\\",\\n      \\\"Excellent written and verbal communication\\\",\\n      \\\"Ability to work collaboratively in cross-functional teams\\\"\\n    ]\\n  }\\n}\\n```\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task4:\\n  Objective: Conduct the technical interview session and record candidate responses\\nTask task5:\\n  Objective: Score the recorded responses using the predefined rubric\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nGenerate technical interview questions and a scoring rubric based on extracted job requirements\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nJSON\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```json\\n{\\n  \\\"technical_interview\\\": {\\n    \\\"questions\\\": [\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 1,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Describe your experience with the Spring Framework. Can you provide examples of how you've used it in past projects?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Spring Framework\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 2,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Explain your approach to designing RESTful APIs. What are some best practices you follow?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"RESTful API Design\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"How do you ensure the quality of your code? Describe your experience with unit testing and other testing methodologies.\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Unit Testing\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Discuss your experience with SQL databases. What are some common challenges you've faced and how did you overcome them?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"SQL Databases\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 5,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Describe your experience with Git. What branching strategies have you used?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Git\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 6,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Explain your understanding of microservices architecture. What are the advantages and disadvantages of using microservices?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Microservices\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 7,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"How do you approach problem-solving and debugging in software development?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Problem-solving\\\",\\n          \\\"Debugging\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n       {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 8,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Describe a complex technical challenge you faced in a previous project and how you resolved it.\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Problem-solving\\\",\\n          \\\"Debugging\\\",\\n          \\\"Software Development\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 9,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Explain your experience working in Agile/Scrum environments. What role did you play, and what were some of the challenges?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Agile/Scrum\\\",\\n          \\\"Collaboration\\\",\\n           \\\"Communication\\\"\\n        ]\\n      },\\n      {\\n        \\\"question_id\\\": 10,\\n        \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Give an example of a time you had to collaborate with a cross-functional team to achieve a technical goal. What were the key aspects of successful collaboration?\\\",\\n        \\\"skills_assessed\\\": [\\n          \\\"Communication\\\",\\n          \\\"Collaboration\\\"\\n        ]\\n      }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"scoring_rubric\\\": {\\n      \\\"criteria\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"criterion_id\\\": 1,\\n          \\\"criterion_name\\\": \\\"Technical Proficiency\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Depth of knowledge and understanding of required technologies (Java, Spring, RESTful APIs, SQL, Git, Microservices)\\\",\\n          \\\"scoring_levels\\\": {\\n            \\\"1\\\": \\\"Limited understanding or experience.\\\",\\n            \\\"2\\\": \\\"Basic understanding; requires guidance.\\\",\\n            \\\"3\\\": \\\"Solid understanding; able to apply knowledge independently.\\\",\\n            \\\"4\\\": \\\"Advanced understanding; demonstrates expertise and can mentor others.\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"criterion_id\\\": 2,\\n          \\\"criterion_name\\\": \\\"Problem-Solving Skills\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Ability to analyze problems, identify root causes, and develop effective solutions.\\\",\\n          \\\"scoring_levels\\\": {\\n            \\\"1\\\": \\\"Struggles to identify and analyze problems.\\\",\\n            \\\"2\\\": \\\"Can identify problems but struggles to develop solutions.\\\",\\n            \\\"3\\\": \\\"Effectively analyzes problems and develops viable solutions.\\\",\\n            \\\"4\\\": \\\"Demonstrates exceptional problem-solving skills and innovative thinking.\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"criterion_id\\\": 3,\\n          \\\"criterion_name\\\": \\\"Communication & Collaboration\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Clarity and effectiveness of communication, and ability to work collaboratively in a team.\\\",\\n          \\\"scoring_levels\\\": {\\n            \\\"1\\\": \\\"Poor communication skills; struggles to collaborate effectively.\\\",\\n            \\\"2\\\": \\\"Adequate communication skills; requires guidance to collaborate effectively.\\\",\\n            \\\"3\\\": \\\"Clear and effective communication; collaborates well with others.\\\",\\n            \\\"4\\\": \\\"Excellent communication skills; proactively fosters collaboration and teamwork.\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"criterion_id\\\": 4,\\n          \\\"criterion_name\\\": \\\"Experience\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Relevance and depth of prior experience to the job requirements.\\\",\\n          \\\"scoring_levels\\\": {\\n            \\\"1\\\": \\\"Limited relevant experience.\\\",\\n            \\\"2\\\": \\\"Some relevant experience, but lacks depth.\\\",\\n            \\\"3\\\": \\\"Solid relevant experience; meets the job requirements.\\\",\\n            \\\"4\\\": \\\"Extensive and highly relevant experience; exceeds the job requirements.\\\"\\n          }\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\\"criterion_id\\\": 5,\\n          \\\"criterion_name\\\": \\\"Code Quality & Testing\\\",\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"Understanding and application of best practices in code quality, including unit testing and debugging.\\\",\\n          \\\"scoring_levels\\\": {\\n            \\\"1\\\": \\\"Little to no understanding of code quality and testing practices.\\\",\\n            \\\"2\\\": \\\"Basic understanding of code quality and testing; requires guidance.\\\",\\n            \\\"3\\\": \\\"Solid understanding and application of code quality and testing practices.\\\",\\n            \\\"4\\\": \\\"Demonstrates expert-level understanding and promotes best practices in code quality and testing.\\\"\\n          }\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  }\\n}\\n```\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-27T16:49:39.025578\"\n}"}
