 \\\"Code Quality & Testing\\\": 4\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"question_id\\\": 8,\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Describe a complex technical challenge you faced in a previous project and how you resolved it.\\\",\\n      \\\"candidate_response\\\": \\\"In a previous project, we had a performance bottleneck in our data processing pipeline. After investigation, we found that the database queries were not optimized for large datasets. We resolved this by redesigning the database schema, adding indexes, and optimizing the queries. We also implemented caching to reduce the load on the database, leading to a significant improvement in performance.\\\",\\n      \\\"scores\\\": {\\n        \\\"Technical Proficiency\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Problem-Solving Skills\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Communication & Collaboration\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Experience\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Code Quality & Testing\\\": 3\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"question_id\\\": 9,\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Explain your experience working in Agile/Scrum environments. What role did you play, and what were some of the challenges?\\\",\\n      \\\"candidate_response\\\": \\\"I have worked in Agile/Scrum environments for several years, primarily as a developer and sometimes as a Scrum master. I participate in sprint planning, daily stand-ups, sprint reviews, and retrospectives. One challenge is ensuring that the team adheres to the Scrum principles and that the product backlog is well-maintained and prioritized.\\\",\\n      \\\"scores\\\": {\\n        \\\"Technical Proficiency\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Problem-Solving Skills\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Communication & Collaboration\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Experience\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Code Quality & Testing\\\": 3\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"question_id\\\": 10,\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Give an example of a time you had to collaborate with a cross-functional team to achieve a technical goal. What were the key aspects of successful collaboration?\\\",\\n      \\\"candidate_response\\\": \\\"I once collaborated with a cross-functional team consisting of developers, designers, and product managers to build a new feature for our mobile app. Key aspects of successful collaboration included clear communication, mutual respect, and a shared understanding of the goals. We used tools like Slack and Jira to facilitate communication and track progress. We also had regular meetings to discuss progress and address any roadblocks.\\\",\\n      \\\"scores\\\": {\\n        \\\"Technical Proficiency\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Problem-Solving Skills\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Communication & Collaboration\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Experience\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Code Quality & Testing\\\": 3\\n      }\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-27T16:50:37.799695\"\n}"}
