xample of a time you had to collaborate with a cross-functional team to achieve a technical goal. What were the key aspects of successful collaboration?\\\",\\n      \\\"candidate_response\\\": \\\"I once collaborated with a cross-functional team consisting of developers, designers, and product managers to build a new feature for our mobile app. Key aspects of successful collaboration included clear communication, mutual respect, and a shared understanding of the goals. We used tools like Slack and Jira to facilitate communication and track progress. We also had regular meetings to discuss progress and address any roadblocks.\\\",\\n      \\\"scores\\\": {\\n        \\\"Technical Proficiency\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Problem-Solving Skills\\\": 3,\\n        \\\"Communication & Collaboration\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Experience\\\": 4,\\n        \\\"Code Quality & Testing\\\": 3\\n      }\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n\\n---\\n# **Downstream Tasks Objectives**\\nTask task7:\\n  Objective: Generate a .txt file documenting all steps taken and send the final evaluation report via email with the .txt attachment\\n\\n---\\n# **Current Task Requirements**\\nCompile a final evaluation report including resume summary and scored responses\\n\\n---\\n\\n# **Required Output Format**\\nPlain text\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"gpt_response\": \"```text\\n1. Analyze the job description.\\n2. Analyze the candidate resume. (INCOMPLETE - Resume content missing.  Cannot proceed with a full analysis.)\\n3. Send an email requesting the candidate's resume.\\n4. Upon receipt of the resume, extract candidate's skills, experience, and education.\\n5. Conduct technical interview.\\n6. Score candidate responses using the predefined rubric. (Scores available from previous task.)\\n7. Compile the final evaluation report.\\n   a.  Include a summary of the candidate's skills, experience, and education (derived from the resume - Step 4).\\n   b.  Include the scored responses from the technical interview.\\n8. Genera